Valadate 0.1.1

  * Fix name of pkg-config file.
  * Fix content of pkg-config file.
  * Load default packages, so .deps file is not needed in the common case.

Valadate 0.1

  * Initial release
  * Runner can execute synchronous, asynchronous and cancellable
    asynchronous tests using both gir and vapi metadata.
  * Runner executes tests with all values of a property provided by
    corresponding generator.
  * Utility functions to wait for async function completion and to wait for
    signal are provided.
  * Utility class for creating a temporary test directory and simple creation
    of files in it is provided.
